description: This skill queries the national weather service to figure out the air quality in a US City. Currently only New York City is supported.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask Air Quality For Air Quality in New York
Alexa, Ask Air Quality What is the air quality in New York
Alexa, Ask Air Quality New York Air Quality
name: Air Quality
shortDescription: This skill queries the national weather service to figure out the air quality in a US City. Currently only New York City is supported.
